#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"            Use the Sign App to manage consent forms, employee contracts, and more !<br/>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"        </strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"            ໃຊ້ແອັບ Sign ເພື່ອຈັດການແບບຟອມການຍິນຍອມ, ສັນຍາພະນັກງານ ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າ"
"ງ!<br/>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"        </strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Appointments App</b>:</strong> Streamline the booking process for pet owners, allowing them to\n"
"                schedule check-ups and surgeries online 24/7.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບການນັດໝາຍ</b>:</strong> ເຮັດໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນການຈອງງ່າຍຂຶ້ນສຳລັບເຈົ້າຂອງສັດລ້ຽງ, ຊ່ວ"
"ຍໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາ\n"
"                ກຳນົດເວລາກວດສຸຂະພາບ ແລະ ການຜ່າຕັດທາງອອນລາຍໄດ້ຕະຫຼອດ 24 ຊົ່ວໂມງ.<br/>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Invoicing App</b>:</strong> Simplify your finances by automatically generating invoices from\n"
"                completed consultations and product sales.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບການອອກໃບບິນ</b>:</strong> ເຮັດໃຫ້ການເງິນຂອງທ່ານງ່າຍຂຶ້ນໂດຍການສ້າງໃບບິນອັດຕ"
"ະໂນມັດຈາກ\n"
"                ການກວດປຶກສາ ແລະ ການຂາຍຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ.<br/>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Marketing App</b>: </strong>Engage your community with targeted email campaigns for vaccination\n"
"                reminders and seasonal health check-ups.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດ</b>: </strong>ສ້າງຄວາມສຳພັນກັບຊຸມຊົນຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍແຄມເປນອີເມວທີ່ກຳນົ"
"ດເປົ້າໝາຍສຳລັບການແຈ້ງເຕືອນ\n"
"                ການສັກຢາວັກຊີນ ແລະ ການກວດສຸຂະພາບຕາມລະດູການ.<br/>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Point of Sale App</b>: </strong>Facilitate a smooth checkout experience by linking consultations and\n"
"                product sales directly to your payment terminal.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບຈຸດຂາຍ (POS)</b>: </strong>ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການຊຳລະເງິນສະດວກສະບາຍໂດຍການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກ"
"ານກວດປຶກສາ ແລະ\n"
"                ການຂາຍຜະລິດຕະພັນໂດຍກົງກັບເຄື່ອງຮັບຊຳລະເງິນຂອງທ່ານ.<br/>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Website App</b>: </strong>Build a professional online presence to market your clinic, share health\n"
"                tips, and attract new pet owners.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບເວັບໄຊ</b>: </strong>ສ້າງຕົວຕົນທາງອອນລາຍທີ່ເປັນມືອາຊີບເພື່ອໂຄສະນາຄລີນິກຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ, ແບ່ງປັນເຄັດລັບ\n"
"                ສຸຂະພາບ ແລະ ດຶງດູດເຈົ້າຂອງສັດລ້ຽງລາຍໃໝ່.<br/>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Tips for Success</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">ເຄັດລັບສູ່ຄວາມສຳເລັດ</span></strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Attachments</strong> store lab results, X‑rays, or referral letters "
"alongside notes in the <strong>Lab Tests &amp; Diagnostics tab</strong>."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໄຟລ໌ຄັດຕິດ</strong> ເກັບຮັກສາຜົນການກວດແລັບ, ຜົນເອກຊະເລ (X-ray), ຫຼື ໜັງສືສົ່ງຕົວ ພ້ອມ"
"ກັບບັນທຶກຕ່າງໆໃນ <strong>ແຖບການກວດແລັບ ແລະ ການວິນິດໄສ</strong>."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automate reminders.</strong> SMS or email nudges cut no‑shows and "
"keep vaccinations on schedule."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນອັດຕະໂນມັດ.</strong> ການສົ່ງ SMS ຫຼື ອີເມວຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດການຜິດນັດ ແລະ ເຮັດໃຫ້ກາ"
"ນສັກວັກຊີນເປັນໄປຕາມກຳນົດເວລາ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automatic confirmations &amp; reminders</strong> via email/SMS keep "
"owners informed."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຢືນຢັນ ແລະ ແຈ້ງເຕືອນອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong> ຜ່ານອີເມວ/SMS ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຈົ້າຂອງສັດລ້ຽງຮັບຊາ"
"ບຂໍ້ມູນສະເໝີ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Barcode &amp; RFID</strong> scanning speeds up product selection."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ບາໂຄດ &amp; RFID</strong> ການສະແກນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເລືອກຜະລິດຕະພັນໄດ້ໄວຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.custom_appointment_info_heading
msgid ""
"<strong>Book an Appointment – Compassionate Care for Your Pets</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຈອງນັດໝາຍ – ການເບິ່ງແຍງດ້ວຍຄວາມໃສ່ໃຈສຳລັບສັດລ້ຽງຂອງທ່ານ</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Booking widget</strong> automatically links to the Appointment app "
"for real‑time availability."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ວິດເຈັດການຈອງ</strong> ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບແອັບການນັດໝາຍໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອເບິ່ງເວລາຫວ່າງແບບສົດ"
"ໆ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Buffer times</strong> between consults prevent overruns."
msgstr "<strong>ເວລາກັນໄວ້</strong> ລະຫວ່າງການກວດຊ່ວຍປ້ອງກັນເວລາທີ່ເກີນກຳນົດ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Custom fields</strong> capture weight, insurance, behavior notes, or"
" anything you need."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຟິວທີ່ກຳນົດເອງ</strong> ໃຊ້ບັນທຶກນ້ຳໜັກ, ປະກັນໄພ, ບັນທຶກພຶດຕິກຳ ຫຼື ສິ່ງອື່ນໆທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Drag‑and‑drop builder</strong> to create service, team, and FAQ "
"pages in minutes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເຄື່ອງມືສ້າງແບບລາກ ແລະ ວາງ</strong> ເພື່ອສ້າງໜ້າບໍລິການ, ທີມງານ ແລະ ຄຳຖາມທີ່ພົບເລື້ອ"
"ຍ (FAQ) ພາຍໃນບໍ່ກີ່ນາທີ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Electronic signatures</strong> accelerate acceptance for surgeries "
"or long‑term care plans."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລາຍເຊັນເອເລັກໂຕຣນິກ</strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການອະນຸມັດການຜ່າຕັດ ຫຼື ແຜນການເບິ່ງແຍງໄລຍະຍາວໄ"
"ວຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Experiment ! </strong>Did you know you can create a copy of your "
"database to try things out ? Simply go to"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ທົດລອງເລີຍ! </strong>ທ່ານຮູ້ບໍ່ວ່າທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງສຳເນົາຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອທົດລອງໃຊ້ງານໄ"
"ດ້? ພຽງແຕ່ໄປທີ່"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Live chat</strong> answers visitor questions and captures leads "
"24/7."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໄລຟ໌ແຊັດ (Live chat)</strong> ຕອບຄຳຖາມຜູ້ເຂົ້າຊົມ ແລະ ເກັບກຳຂໍ້ມູນລູກຄ້າໄດ້ຕະຫຼອດ "
"24 ຊົ່ວໂມງ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Lot/serial tracking</strong> meets pharmaceutical compliance."
msgstr "<strong>ການຕິດຕາມເລກລັອດ/ຊີຣຽວ</strong> ຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມຂໍ້ກຳນົດທາງດ້ານການຢາ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Multiple payment methods</strong> (cash, card, vouchers) in one "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຮູບແບບການຊຳລະເງິນທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ</strong> (ເງິນສົດ, ບັດ, ບັດຂອງຂວັນ) ໃນໜ້າຈໍດຽວ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Multiple units</strong> (dose, box, bottle) with automatic "
"conversions."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຫຼາຍຫົວໜ່ວຍ</strong> (ໂດສ, ກ່ອງ, ແກ້ວ) ພ້ອມລະບົບການແປງຫົວໜ່ວຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>One‑click product picker</strong> adds vaccines or meds directly to "
"the visit through the <strong>catalog</strong>."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການເລືອກຜະລິດຕະພັນໃນຄລິກດຽວ</strong> ເພີ່ມວັກຊີນ ຫຼື ຢາໂດຍກົງໃສ່ໃນການມາພົບ ຜ່ານ "
"<strong>ແຄັດຕາລັອກ</strong>."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>One‑click quotation</strong> from consultation converts to invoice "
"or POS ticket."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃນຄລິກດຽວ</strong> ຈາກການກວດປຶກສາ ສາມາດປ່ຽນເປັນໃບບິນ ຫຼື ບິນ "
"POS ໄດ້ທັນທີ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Online calendar</strong> shows real‑time slots for each vet or room."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ປະຕິທິນອອນລາຍ</strong> ສະແດງເວລາຫວ່າງແບບສົດໆສຳລັບສັດຕະວະແພດ ຫຼື ຫ້ອງກວດແຕ່ລະຫ້ອ"
"ງ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Appointment app enables self‑service booking, calendar sync, and"
" effortless follow‑ups.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບການນັດໝາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຈອງເອງໄດ້, ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ປະຕິທິນ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມຜົນໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍ"
"ດາຍ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Consultation sheets record symptoms, vitals, and actions while "
"keeping the vet’s workflow fluid.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໃບບັນທຶກການກວດຂອງພວກເຮົາຊ່ວຍບັນທຶກອາການ, ສັນຍານຊີບ ແລະ ການປິ່ນປົວ ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ກາ"
"ນເຮັດວຽກຂອງແພດຄ່ອງຕົວ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our POS lets receptionists scan, split bills, and print "
"receipts—while stock levels adjust instantly.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບ POS ຂອງພວກເຮົາຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ພະນັກງານຕ້ອນຮັບສະແກນ, ແຍກບິນ ແລະ ພິມໃບບິນໄດ້—ໃນຂະນະທີ່ລ"
"ະບົບສະຕັອກຈະປັບປ່ຽນທັນທີ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Pet records feature centralizes identity, vaccination status, "
"and allergies for safer treatments.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບປະຫວັດສັດລ້ຽງຂອງພວກເຮົາລວບລວມຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຕົນ, ປະຫວັດວັກຊີນ ແລະ ຂໍ້ມູນການແພ້ ເພື່ອການປິ່ນ"
"ປົວທີ່ປອດໄພກວ່າ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Product management keeps pricing, barcodes, and expiry dates "
"accurate across sales channels.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຈັດການຜະລິດຕະພັນຂອງພວກເຮົາຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ລາຄາ, ບາໂຄດ ແລະ ວັນໝົດອາຍຸຖືກຕ້ອງໃນທຸກຊ່ອງທາງກ"
"ານຂາຍ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Sales app groups treatments, products, and services into neat "
"documents owners trust.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບການຂາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາລວບລວມການປິ່ນປົວ, ຜະລິດຕະພັນ ແລະ ບໍລິການ ເຂົ້າເປັນເອກະສານທີ່ເປັນ"
"ລະບຽບ ເພື່ອສ້າງຄວາມເຊື່ອໝັ້ນໃຫ້ແກ່ເຈົ້າຂອງສັດລ້ຽງ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Website app lets you publish pages, embed booking widgets, and "
"convert visitors into appointments.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບເວັບໄຊຂອງພວກເຮົາຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເຜີຍແຜ່ໜ້າເວັບ, ຝັງວິດເຈັດການຈອງ ແລະ ປ່ຽນຜູ້ເຂົ້າຊົມໃຫ້ເປັນ"
"ການນັດໝາຍ.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Owner relationship</strong> connects contact details for billing and"
" reminders."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄວາມສຳພັນກັບເຈົ້າຂອງ</strong> ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລາຍລະອຽດຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ສຳລັບການອອກໃບບິນ ແລະ ການແຈ້ງເ"
"ຕືອນ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Payment terms</strong> handle deposits, installments, or immediate "
"pay."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເງື່ອນໄຂການຊຳລະເງິນ</strong> ຈັດການເງິນມັດຈຳ, ການຜ່ອນຊຳລະ ຫຼື ການຈ່າຍທັນທີ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Price lists &amp; promos</strong> support wellness plans or "
"discounted packages."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລາຍການລາຄາ &amp; ໂປຣໂມຊັນ</strong> ຮອງຮັບແຜນການເບິ່ງແຍງສຸຂະພາບ ຫຼື ແພັກເກັດສ່ວນ"
"ຫຼຸດ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Real‑time sync</strong> with accounting and inventory for zero "
"re‑entry."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຊິງຄ໌ຂໍ້ມູນແບບສົດໆ</strong> ກັບລະບົບບັນຊີ ແລະ ສະຕັອກສິນຄ້າ ເພື່ອຫຼຸດການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຊ້ຳຊ້ອນ."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Reorder rules</strong> trigger purchase orders before you run out."
msgstr ""
